    "To ensure fast RealTimeKernel-based computations, we devised an adaptive thresholding scheme resulting in sparse transition matrices.",
    "Transition probabilities falling below a certain threshold are set to zero, all others are kept unchanged.",
    "Per default, we identify the smallest threshold τ that does not remove all transitions for any cell, that is",
